.SH LISTEN COMMAND SYNTAX
.SS Instruct ldmsd to listen to a port
.sp
\fBlisten\fP \fBport\fP=\fIPORT\fP
\fBxprt\fP=\fIsock\fP|\fIrdma\fP|\fIugni\fP|\fIfabric\fP
