[\fBrx_rate\fP=\fIRX_RATE\fP]
.TP
.B \fBport\fP=\fIPORT\fP
.nf

The port to listen to. Also, please be sure not to use ephemeral
port (ports in the range of
\fB/proc/sys/net/ip4/ip_local_port_range\fP).
.fi
.sp
.TP
